4.0. TASK ENDPOINTS

4.1. Create a Task

POST
…./api/tasks/projects/:projectId/tasks
Creates a task 


Request Body:

Field
Type
Description
title
string
Required. Task title.
description
string
Required. Full description of what needs to be done.
project_id
integer
Required. ID of the parent project.
due_date
date
Required. ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DD.
estimated_hours
integer
Required. Estimated hours to complete the task.
volunteer_ids
array
Required. Array of volunteer IDs. Maximum 5.


